headline: Netflix Reportedly Prepares All-Cash Bid For Warner Bros. As Paramount Turns Up Heat On Takeover Battle
summary: Netflix Inc. (NASDAQ:NFLX) is reportedly preparing to revise the terms of its $82.7 billion deal to buy Warner Bros. Discovery (NASDAQ:WBD) to make it an all-cash offer, as it seeks to fend off Paramount Skydance’s (NASDAQ:PSKY) hostile bid. The revised deal, aimed at offering WBD shareholders a quicker and simpler transaction, is still under negotiation and may change, the Financial Times reported on Tuesday, citing people familiar with the matter.
